data.description: Beautifully updated spacious brick dwelling boasting 3,320 sq. ft. 6 bedrooms and 3.5 baths with fully finished basement. The Master en suite offers a full bathroom and an impressive walk-in closet. Enter into the lovely foyer and experience the unique balance of open concept and and closed concept. This home has lots of natural light and space for entertaining. This property is a true gem waiting to be discovered. Come see it today!
